Data

Class OrderedPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • Data.OrderedPackage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class OrderedPackage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class implements the Ordered Package entity with the attributes id, packaging, price, order. This class represents an Ordered Package. This entity class is Serializable. Allowing this entity to be written as an object into a text file.
